data.description: Welcome to 1763 Forest Dr! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is situated walking distance from the water and just minutes from local shopping centers and amenities. Featuring a fully fenced yard, ensuring privacy and security for your pets and loved ones. With the 2-car garage and level-to-street driveway, you have ample parking space to park vehicles and river toys. Your dream home awaits by the Colorado River!
